<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Testimonials Section</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <section class="testimonials text-center bg-light py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="mb-5 font-weight-bold">What people are saying...</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="testimonial-item mx-auto mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                        <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle mb-3" src="https://github.com/StartBootstrap/startbootstrap-landing-page/blob/master/dist/assets/img/testimonials-1.jpg?raw=true" alt="Margaret">
                        <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Margaret E.</h5>
                        <p class="font-weight-light mb-0">"This is fantastic! Thanks so much guys!"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="testimonial-item mx-auto mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                        <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle mb-3" src="https://github.com/StartBootstrap/startbootstrap-landing-page/blob/master/dist/assets/img/testimonials-2.jpg?raw=true" alt="Fred">
                        <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Fred S.</h5>
                        <p class="font-weight-light mb-0">"Bootstrap is amazing. I've been using it to create lots of super nice landing pages."</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="testimonial-item mx-auto mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                        <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle mb-3" src="https://github.com/StartBootstrap/startbootstrap-landing-page/blob/master/dist/assets/img/testimonials-3.jpg?raw=true" alt="Sarah">
                        <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Sarah W.</h5>
                        <p class="font-weight-light mb-0">"Thanks so much for making these free resources available to us!"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
